  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a deep fryer or a large pot to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Prepare the tod rice mixture by combining it with scrambled eggs, chopped cilantro, and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "Using a spoon, drop the mixture by tablespoonfuls into the hot oil, being careful not to overcrowd the pot.",
    "Fry the tod for 2-3 minutes or until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Using a slotted spoon, remove the fried tod from the oil and drain on paper towels.",
    "In a small saucepan, heat the HP sauce over low heat.",
    "To serve, place the fried tod on a plate and drizzle with the warmed HP sauce.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
